snippet.title: EverQuest: Ring of Scale [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
Join us for the Ring of Scale expansion! Learn more at: http://bit.ly/EQ-RoS

Play EverQuest for FREE! https://www.everquest.com/register

Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EverQuestLive
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/everquest

Return to Kunark and aid the Combine as they face off against the Sarnak Empire and the Ring of Scale. What will become of the Sarnak Empire? Will dragons reign supreme over Norrath? Only the most powerful of heroes will be able to help the Combine to breach the heart of Veeshan’s Peak. Hurry back to Kunark to witness what becomes of the Combine in this epic conclusion of EverQuest’s latest adventure.
